uccessfully put into place painful adjustment measures.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aPopular musicxHistory and criticism. 0aIntertextuality. 4aElectronic books.1 aBurkholder, J. Peterq(James Peter),eauthor of foreword.1 aBurns, Lori,eeditor.1 aLacasse, Serge,eeditor.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher. 0aTracking pop.40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.9755813